element.name: have a seat in kill by trackhead, Traditional Cache (1/1)
element.description: very easy, in the lovely village of kill. home to the 2003 special olympics Don't worry to much about windows across the road, they know the cache is there and like to keep an eye on it!!!
element.long-description: small lunch box, wrapped in black bin liner.
